Item 5.02 Departure of Director or Principal Officers; Election of Directors; Appointment of Principal Officers
 
On June 10, 2005, the Board of Directors (the "Board") of Advent Software Inc. (the "Company") elected A. George Battle to the Board of Advent. Mr. Battle has also been elected to serve on the Corporate Governance and Nominating Committee of the Board.
 
Item 5.03 Amendments to Articles of Incorporation or Bylaws; Changes in Fiscal Year
 
On June 10, 2005 and effective as of such date, Advent's Board approved an amendment to Section 3.2 of the Company's Bylaws to increase the membership of the Board from six to seven members in connection with the election of Mr. Battle to the Company's Board. The amended and restated Bylaws of the Company are attached and filed as Exhibit 3.1 to this current report on Form 8-K.
 
