ITEM 8.01 Other Events
 
On December 2, 2005, Advent Software, Inc. (the "Company") signed a definitive agreement to sell its Advent Hellas subsidiary, with assets of approximately $106,000 and liabilities of approximately $17,000, to its current management for proceeds of approximately $22,000. The Company currently expects to record a gain on sale of approximately $0.2 million in the fourth quarter of 2005, which supersedes its initial estimate of a gain of approximately $1.8 million previously disclosed in in the Company's Quarterly Report on Form 10-Q for the quarter ended September 30, 2005 filed on November 9, 2005. 
