.  Notwithstanding anything to the contrary above, Tenant's right to terminate this Lease pursuant to the above shall, at Landlord's option, be inapplicable if, at the time of delivery of Tenant's Termination Notice, or on the Early Termination Date, there exists an uncured Event of Default under the Lease, or if Tenant fails to pay the entire Termination Fee required hereunder.
