The successful business operation and reputation of Advent is built upon the principles of fair dealing and ethical conduct of our officers, employees and directors.  Our reputation for integrity and excellence requires careful observance of the spirit and letter of all applicable laws and regulations, as well as a scrupulous regard for the highest standards of conduct and personal integrity.
 
Advent will comply with all applicable laws and regulations and expects its officers, employees to conduct business in accordance with the letter, spirit, and intent of all relevant laws and to refrain from any illegal, dishonest, or unethical conduct.
