Compliance with this policy of business ethics and conduct is the responsibility of every Advent director, officer and employee Because some of the principles described in this Code of Business Ethics and Conduct policy are general in nature, you should review all applicable Advent policies and procedures located at our intranet site, the Gate, for specific instructions, and contact the Vice President of Human Resources or Chief Financial Officer if you have any questions.
