c.
                                      
Additionally, we shall seek approval from the compensation committee to provide for a 12 month exercise period following termination for vested Stock Settled SARs, if you have also qualified for severance benefits under the Plan.
 
This offer of employment contains all of the terms and conditions of your employment with Advent and supersedes any and all prior oral or written representations or agreements made by anyone employed by or associated with Advent.   The terms of this offer, if accepted, will become your terms of employment and can only be added to or modified by a written document signed by myself or an executive management team member.
 
