401(K) PLAN
                              
 
Tamale sponsors a 401(k) Plan to provide retirement benefits for its US employees. The plan provides tax-deferred salary deductions for eligible employees. Employees may contribute a percentage of their compensation to this Plan, limited by an annual maximum amount as determined by the Internal Revenue Service. The Company did not make any matching contributions for the years ended December 31, 2007 and 2006.
 
