condenser water allocated for Tenant's use to the amount necessary to supply Tenant's requirements as evidenced by Tenant's condenser water use for the prior twelve (12) month period.  In addition, if Tenant fails to connect to the condenser water system within twelve (12) months after the Rent Commencement Date, Landlord shall not be required to make available to Tenant any condenser water.
