Article 19
 
19.06
                    
Landlord will not carry insurance of any kind on Tenant's Property and improvements and betterments, and shall not be obligated to repair any damage to or replace Tenant's Property, improvements or betterments.  Tenant agrees to look to its own insurance for
 
