of the Disclosure Schedule, membership interests of the Company are free and clear of any pledge, lien, security interest, encumbrance, claim or equitable interest, and are not subject to preemptive rights, rights of first refusal, rights of first offer or similar rights created by statute, the Operating Agreement or any agreement to which the Company is a party or to which it is bound.  All of the issued and outstanding Company Units have been offered, issued and sold by the Company in compliance with all applicable federal and state securities or "blue sky" Laws.  There is no indebtedness having the right to vote on any matters on which the Members may vote.
 
