of the Disclosure Schedule, the Company has not received notice from any Person claiming that such operation or any act, any Company Product and Service or Technology of the Company infringes or misappropriates any Intellectual Property Rights of any Person or constitutes unfair competition or trade practices under the laws of any jurisdiction (nor, to the Knowledge of the Company, is there any basis therefor).
 
