provided that
(iii)
                                                
All audits or other controversies in respect of Taxes that could give rise to an obligation of the Unitholders and/or Optionholders to indemnify the Company, the Surviving Company or Parent under this Agreement (whether administrative or judicial) shall be conducted in accordance with the provisions of .
