Item 5.02 Departure of Directors or Certain Officers; Election of Directors; Appointment of Certain Officers; Compensatory Arrangements of Certain Officers
 
On September 8, 2011, the Board of Directors (the "Board") of Advent Software, Inc. ("Advent" or the "Company") elected Mr. Asiff Hirji to the Board of Advent to be effective as of September 14, 2011.  It has not yet been determined on which committees of the Board Mr. Hirji will serve as a member.
 
Item 5.03 Amendments to Articles of Incorporation or Bylaws; Changes in Fiscal Year
 
On September 8, 2011 and effective as of September 14, 2011, Advent's Board approved an amendment to Section 3.2 of the Company's Bylaws to increase the membership of the Board from six to seven members in connection with the election of Mr. Hirji to the Company's Board.  The amended and restated Bylaws of the Company are attached and filed as Exhibit 3.1 to this current report on Form 8-K.
 
