7.16
                       
Amendments to Organizational Documents
.  Amend, modify or otherwise change the charter, articles of incorporation, partnership agreement, by-laws or other organizational documents of the Loan Parties to the extent such amendment, modification, waiver or other change would reasonably be expected to impair the ability of the Loan Parties to perform their obligations under the Loan Documents.
 
